62
00:05:25,010 --> 00:05:27,610
<i>This weekend is all about the two of us.</i>

63
00:05:28,550 --> 00:05:30,510
<i>I'm a happy man.</i>

64
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:33,220
♫ ♫

65
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:34,710
So cute.

66
00:05:34,710 --> 00:05:37,590
♫ ♫

67
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:40,930
♫ ♫

68
00:05:40,930 --> 00:05:42,950
What's your pick? Vanilla, or chocolate?

69
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:45,520
[Winter Ice Pancake - Vanilla or Chocolate]
That's a hard question.

70
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:49,660
<i>Then let's just get both, and share them.</i>

71
00:05:49,660 --> 00:05:51,740
♫ ♫

